  "intent_precise": "Illumina DNA Prep Part 3, Amplify Tagmented DNA: Using cycler_plate (plate, slot 2), thermo_tubes (labware, slot 3), index_plate (pcr_plate, slot 3), sample_plate (deep_well_plate, slot 6). With temperature module, magnetic module. (1) Engage magnets for bead separation. (2) Incubate for 3 minutes. (3) Transfer from source to destination. (4) Disengage magnets to release beads. (5) Mix 5 times at 30\u00b5L in pcr_mix A1. (6) Transfer from source to destination. (7) Mix 10 times at 40\u00b5L. (8) Transfer from source to destination. (9) Pause: Please centrifuge plate in slot 2 at 280 x g for 3 seconds, return to slot 2 when done (10) Transfer from source to destination. (11) Transfer from source to destination. (12) Mix 10 times at 40\u00b5L. (13) Pause: Run complete, please move sample plate to off-deck thermocycler",
  "intent_concise": "Perform magnetic bead separation. (volumes 10\u00b5L-60\u00b5L)",
  "intent": "For the Illumina DNA Prep Part 3 amplification step, start by engaging the magnets on your magnetic module and let the beads separate for 3 minutes, then transfer your samples and release the magnets. You'll need to do some mixing - first 5 times at 30\u00b5L in pcr_mix well A1, then after the next transfer, mix 10 times at 40\u00b5L. Take a quick pause to centrifuge the plate in slot 2 at 280 x g for just 3 seconds and return it, then do your final transfers and mix 10 times at 40\u00b5L again before moving the sample plate to your off-deck thermocycler to complete the run.",
